text: Saying a special prayer tonight for families of those unarmed and killed by police. Rather innocent or guilty, too many names, many unknown & not mentioned. author: Dr. JaKyta Lawrie
text: Yes, All Lives Matter, however we are in a movement about black lives, inequities, and systematic racism. It’s about the black lives murdered by racist police officers and racist white people. Its about the fear I have for my black sons. It’s okay to say black lives matter. #BLM

author: Dr. JaKyta Lawrie
text: Heavy 💔! Senseless murder! Hard to stay positive when it’s so blatant. I have black sons, raised well. Lord forbid if they make a mistake, wrong place-wrong time, right place-wrong kind. Value of a black man’s life continues to be devalued. Dinner talk was hard tonight 😞🙏🏽
